 and I used to have to walk to it and take them there and bring them back to the shop and we used to work until round about 8 o'clock on Mo
nday, Tuesday and Wednesday, half day was Thursday, 1 o'clock, Friday night it would be half past 9 and Saturday night it would be about half past }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15417867\charrsid4203662 11}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14698603\charrsid4203662 . }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 We used to have supper at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15417867\charrsid4203662 10}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 
