 we had black pudding from the butchers shop across the way which I think the lady assistant was well in with the son of the butchers you see and every other week we used to have black pudding and she used to fetch some rolls, or I had some bread rolls, s
o
mething like that, and the other week we had chips. And this shoe shop I worked for they had stacks and stacks of shoes outside on sticks, pairs of shoes. And my job was to see that none of them were pinched. And apart from that was to try to sell them. A
nd I'd get a customer and ask him what size boots he wanted and I would take them in and then the Manager used to wrap them up and sell them you see and then I used to stand outside again. You could get mens}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15417867\charrsid4203662 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662  working boots, hob nail boots for 3/11-halfd. a pair. Then after that -
