 years between me eldest sister and me eldest brother and then this sister that is living that is 80, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698603\charrsid4203662 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 
 years between me eldest brother and this sister. And }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698603\charrsid4203662 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662  years between the engine driver and this sister. And }{\rtlch\fcs1 
