{\xmlattrvalue 0}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 12}}}midday{\*\xmlclose} meal at home, wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Yes, oh, there was no school meals then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Who would there be at home for that meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Probably the brother older than myself and myself and my sister, and mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 What about your evening meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Well, evening meals, er, as we came in, I think, as we came in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 What sort of things would you have in an evening, what sort of food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Oh, jam, maybe, er, mother sometimes made, er
, potato cakes, usually once a week she used to do a lot of potatoes, you know, and lot them, some of them go cold and mash them up, and she used to make potato cakes, and she used to bake them, in the oven and, er, we used to have them warm with butter o
n them.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 What sort of an oven had you? Was it a gas oven or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Er, a gas oven later, and previous to that the oven in a range one of the old black iron ranges that there used to be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Was your father's food any different from the food which the children had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 No, my f-, I don't think so, only probably more of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 What about your mother, would she eat the same as you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 My Mother? Well, if anyone went short, I think it was my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Did anybody ever say grace at mealtimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Would your mother expect you to eat everything she gave you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Yes, I do-, I don't think we refused anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Would you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Sometimes. If we were hungry, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Would you get it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Yes, yes, I-, if it was there to be got, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Did your mother expect you to hold your knife and fork in a certain way, or sit up straight at the table?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Yes, yes, yes, I re-, I re-, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname State}}nev-{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, never remember being allowed to slop about, and you know, make a mess.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 When there were several of you in for a meal, did you always sit at the same places round the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 What order would your mother serve you in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Oh, I don't know, I don't know, maybe youngest first, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Was your mother an easy person to get on with, would you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 
Yes, very easy, and if you talked to the neighbours down the street, actually she died in this house, er, she would talk to the neighbours down the s-street, er, I think you would find that everyo
ne like her, and had a good word for her, because at that time, er, at that time she was always willing to go out, out and help, er, in deaths, laying people out and that sort of thing, for which she never expected payment, and, and didn't get any, I don'
t think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Was she the sort of mother that showed affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 If you had worries as a child, would you be able to go and talk to her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Oh, yes, oh, yes, certainly.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 What sort of behaviour did your mother expect from you as children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 
Well, I don't think she, she minded noise, but she expected us to be, I suppose, like any-, anyone else, you know, er, not knock the place about or, or anything like that, but, as far as I can remember, if the weather was decent, or, or
 even if it wasn't decent, we were outside until, one of, the big ones came in and said, come on, time for bed or something like that. When we were in, o-, of course, we probably fell quiet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Did your mother bring you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in certain ways? I mean, how would she expect you to treat them?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 
Er, no, I think we all got on together; there was no falling out, or anything of that description, I don't remember, er, er, th-, the problem was at times when we had bit o
f a barney among ourselves but, er, I don't remember, no-, nothing of any importance, anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Do you think your mother brought you up to think of certain things as being most important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15417867\charrsid4203662 She expected us to be decent with other people and to lead, lead a decent life}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4203662  }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5718944\charrsid4203662 ourselves,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15417867\charrsid4203662  that's all I can say. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 
W-, we went to Sunday School, we went to church, and I think I told you, my mother was a member of the Mothers' Union, she was a churchwoman and the parson used to come more or less every week, usually tea time, have a cup of tea.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 What was your mother's attitude towards swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 
Well, I don't really know, just the same time I can't tell you whether she swore or whether she didn't. I don't think she did, but I wouldn't be sure.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 I wondered if you were ever punished as a child for using swear words which you'd picked up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15417867\charrsid4203662 (interviewee) I don't, don't, I don't remember, no.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 What sort of things were you punished for, if you were naughty as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Oh, if we didn't come
back to time or if we'd been told, say to come in to go for an errand we didn't come in, all that sort of thing, might get a scuff across the earhole or something like that, but that's all, I never remember my mother hitting any of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 Were birthdays anything special in your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10751724 JH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 
Not particularly. There was probably a present, I never remember it, it wouldn't be much because there was never the money there and, we never, we never had, I don't remember having a birthday party, you know, or anything like that. Christmastime, yes.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14504576 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662 What was Christmas like?
