gs, she used to make her own mince meat, and of course she used to make the cake, and, er, mince pies and all that, that sort of thing. We, we didn't have poultry or anything like that, probably, er, leg of pork or something like that, but something that 
was, would, y-, you know last for }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698603\charrsid4203662 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15412957\charrsid4203662  or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698603\charrsid4203662 4}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
