f those, and, er, we had several records, and in the end, I, I think it was given to the rag and bone man, something like that, i-, it would probably have been worth a pound or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14698603\charrsid4203662 2}{
